{"tid":1351830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有人入黎同我聽住 唔好再輕生","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:47.000Z","uid":138296,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9daea1008b8f3608aaaad47ec31c3df14637e13b","tid":1351830,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"我知大家好憤怒好絕望，睇住手足比人打、警黑合作。但呢個唔係終結黎架。仲有好多人係我地背後支持我地，前線、後排、物資、記者、不同各界既人都想香港好。都唔忍心你地就咁自殺。每多你一份能力 就多一個機會推翻暴政。如果覺得好攰 就唔好再接觸任何媒體 好好休息下 去下旅行。我地會好好咁幫你行落去，到你覺得無問題。我地再一齊撐落去啦！"},{"pid":"2d2781aa1760599abb78f33eb1efc3c33893b755","tid":1351830,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"228faf8b0bde507bd5964ffcbc2f680eb1456b66","tid":1351830,"uid":138296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"每一個都好重要"},{"pid":"f94b75b71c892262c7486d0639f4bd55fa7ac2ca","tid":1351830,"uid":150742,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"珍惜生命 香港人漸覺醒 我們已看見曙光 我地會贏 你地可唔可以應承我同我一齊見證香港人打贏呢場仗嘅一日？"},{"pid":"c5a4e3a278e877fabf9394f8d76b1eff92685f33","tid":1351830,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"670ec11e935a4f108a18fe2238ed4694af73b834","tid":1351830,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"搵信得過既朋友傾下計！"},{"pid":"a1afed017bf9a01697077535967d9de2ca81df12","tid":1351830,"uid":49028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n各位手足，唔好忘記上環既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGQaJo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGQaJo2.png&h=6493ab81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[文宣] 我朋友整左幾幅圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346320\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{